{"name": "odoo14-addon-openupgrade-scripts", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-openupgrade-scripts", "version": "14.0.1.0.1", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/openupgrade", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Module that contains all the migrations analysis and scripts for migrate Odoo SA modules.", "upload_time": 1640682792}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2FOpenUpgrade-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/OpenUpgrade\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/OpenUpgrade/tree/14.0/openupgrade_scripts\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/OpenUpgrade-14-0/OpenUpgrade-14-0-openupgrade_scripts\n    ```\n  maintainer-MiquelRForgeFlow: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/MiquelRForgeFlow.png?size=40px\n    :alt: MiquelRForgeFlow\n    :target: https://github.com/MiquelRForgeFlow\n    ```\n  maintainer-StefanRijnhart: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/StefanRijnhart.png?size=40px\n    :alt: StefanRijnhart\n    :target: https://github.com/StefanRijnhart\n    ```\n  maintainer-pedrobaeza: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/pedrobaeza.png?size=40px\n    :alt: pedrobaeza\n    :target: https://github.com/pedrobaeza\n    ```\n---\n\n# Openupgrade Scripts\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }}\n\nThis module is a containers of migration script to migrate from 13.0 to 14.0 version.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Installation\n\nThis module does not need to be installed on a database.\nIt simply needs to be available via your `addons-path`.\n\n## Configuration\n\n- call your odoo instance with the option `--upgrade-path=/PATH_TO_openupgrade_scripts_MODULE/scripts/`\n\nor\n\n- add the key to your configuration file:\n\n```shell\n[options]\nupgrade_path = /PATH_TO_openupgrade_scripts_MODULE/scripts/\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/OpenUpgrade/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/OpenUpgrade/issues/new?body=module:%20openupgrade_scripts%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Sylvain LE GAL \\<<https://twitter.com/legalsylvain>>\n- Stefan Rijnhart \\<<mailto:stefan@opener.am>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainers](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-MiquelRForgeFlow }} {{ maintainer-StefanRijnhart }} {{ maintainer-pedrobaeza }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/OpenUpgrade](https://github.com/OCA/OpenUpgrade/tree/14.0/openupgrade_scripts) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.apriori", "documentation": ["Encode any known changes to the database here\nto help the matching process"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.apriori.renamed_modules", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.apriori.merged_modules", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.apriori.renamed_models", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.apriori.merged_models", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.scripts.account.14.0.1.1.pre-migration", "documentation": ["Copyright 2021 ForgeFlow S.L.  <https://www.forgeflow.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [{"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.scripts.account.14.0.1.1.pre-migration.rename_fields", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "env", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.scripts.account.14.0.1.1.pre-migration.m2m_tables_account_journal_renamed", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "env", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.scripts.account.14.0.1.1.pre-migration.remove_constrains_reconcile_models", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "env", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.openupgrade_scripts.scripts.account.14.0.1.1.pre-migration.copy_fields", "asynch